properties.name: id
properties.comment: The unique identifier of this object

properties.name: ownerCustomer
properties.comment: Contains the owner ref of the consultation (either a customer or a group).

properties.name: customer
properties.comment: Contains the single owner of the consultation. If the consultations belongs to a customer group the owners are in customers. Either this or customers must be set.

properties.name: customers
properties.comment: Contains all the customers if this is a consultation for a group. If this property is used (non empty) the customer property must be nil. And the customers property must be used.

properties.name: customerGroup
properties.comment: If customers contains more than one element this property must not be null and ownerCustomer needs to reference to this group.
